casebody.data:
The Florida Midland, &c., Co., Respondent, v. Edwin E. Glashin, Appellant. Decided June 14, 1886. Appeal from order setting *544aside order of reference. Ira Shafer, for appellant. Charles B. Meyer, for respondent.

Before Sedgwick, Ch. J. and Truax, J.

Opinion by Sedgwick, Ch. J. Order reversed; motion below denied. Defendant to have $10 costs.
